P(A \vert B) = P(A \cap B)/P(B) = P(B/A) \times P(A)/P(B)
P(X = 1 \vert X+Y = 4) = P(X+Y=4 \,\,\& \,\, X=1)/P(X+Y = 4)
P(X+Y=4 \,\,\& \,\, X=1) = P(X=1 \,\,\& \,\, Y=3) = P(X=1)P(Y=3)
P(X+Y = 4) = \sum_{k=0}^4P(X=k)P(Y=4-k)
